MCM2 bug-reports

#1

**Summary:**
Age limit filter doesn't recognise '14' as valid age to continue survey, (A3).

**Environment:**
Android 5.1.1 Xiaomi Redmi Note 3 (Root)

**Preconditions:**
Syrex MCM2 app is installed & launched.

**Steps to reproduce:**
1) Launch MCM2 app;
2) Log in;
3) Scan coupon;
4) Fill valid data into the fields: "UIC", "Возраст", "Пол";
5) Tap on the [Далее] button;  
6) Tap on the [Пройти анкетирование] button;
7) Input "14" into the field: "A3";
8) Observe result.

**Actual result:**
Age limit filter doesn't recognise '14' as valid age to continue survey

**Expected result:**
You're able to continue srvey.

#2

**Summary:**
There is no [Сканировать] button while registration of new coupon.

**Environment:**
Android 5.1.1 Xiaomi Redmi Note 3 (Root)

**Preconditions:**
Syrex MCM2 app is installed & launched.

**Steps to reproduce:**
1) Launch MCM2 app;
2) Log in;
3) Scan coupon;
4) Fill valid data into the fields: "UIC", "Возраст", "Пол";
5) Tap on the [Далее] button;
6) Tap on the [Выдать купоны] button;
7) Read the instruction;
8) Observe result.

**Actual result:**
There is no [Сканировать] button.

**Expected result:**
There is no [+Добавить] button.

**Additional info:**
It may be a typo in instruction because [+Добавить] button function as [Сканировать] button.

#3

**Summary:**
There is no input field displayed with 'Other (specify)' option, (A14).

**Environment:**
Android 5.1.1 Xiaomi Redmi Note 3 (Root)

**Preconditions:**
Syrex MCM2 app is installed & launched.

**Steps to reproduce:**
1) Launch MCM2 app;
2) Log in;
3) Scan coupon;
4) Fill valid data into the fields: "UIC", "Возраст", "Пол";
5) Tap on the [Далее] button;  
6) Tap on the [Пройти анкетирование] button;
7) Input "<14 number" into the field: "A3";
8) Tap on [А14. What is your main occupation now?];
9) Select 'Other (specify)' option from drop-down list;
10) Observe result.

**Actual result:**
There is no input field displayed with 'Other (specify)' option.

**Expected result:**
There is input field displayed with 'Other (specify)' option.

#4

**Summary:**
At attempt to input invalid data into login fields authentication error message is displayed in English

**Environment:**
Android 5.1.1 Xiaomi Redmi Note 3 (Root)

**Preconditions:**
Syrex MCM2 app is installed & launched.

**Steps to reproduce:**
1) Launch MCM2 app;
2) Fill log in fields with invalid data;
3) Press [Войти] button;
4) Observe result.

**Actual result:**
Authentication error message is displayed in English.

**Expected result:**
Authentification error message is displayed in Russian.